---
title: Sri Lankan-Spiced Lentil, Chicken & Veggie Soup with Yoghurt & Cheesy Garlic Flatbreads
description: Having all the flavours and textures of veggies, chicken, lentils and spices melting into one delectable soup is the perfect way to finish
off a day. You might notice the odd hint of ginger in the creaminess of the soup or perhaps notes of our Sri Lankan spice blend.
Enjoy by dipping the cheesy naan in the soup to soak it up.
